  <name>Irodori Table</name>
  <summary>Open-source SQL workbench for multiple database engines</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Irodori Table is a local-first desktop database workbench for SQL editing,
      schema inspection, result browsing, query planning, import/export, and
      extension-ready database connectivity.
    </p>
    <p>
      This is a development preview. Review SQL, target connections, and backups
      before running destructive commands.
    </p>
  </description>
